🗒️ Usage instructions
*When launched, you’ll see a welcome screen to select Employee (Admin) or Customer.

*Admins can:
-Login using admin credentials.
-Manage customer accounts (create/delete).
-Manage admin accounts (create/delete).
-Check customer summaries.

*Customers can:
-Login using account number and PIN.
-Deposit or withdraw money (with limits).
-Check balance.
-Change PIN.
-Close their account.

⚖️ Limitations & notes
*Data is stored in plain text files under database/, so it is not suitable for production-level security.

*No encryption of sensitive data (PINs, credentials).

*Only supports single-user at a time due to file-based storage.
